Class ModelProxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • progetto.network.proxy.ModelProxy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IModel, ObservableModel

    public class ModelProxy
extends java.lang.Object
implements ObservableModel
    Author:
    Massimo proxy of the whole model, it is able to clone another observable model so that immutable object can be created.
